    "summary": "Implemented the Group A additive new-ui-evaluation slice: isolated React/Vite TypeScript preview app, fixture-backed read-only Python adapter, typed fixture contract covering operator views and diagnostics, UI and adapter tests, operator documentation, and completed matching OpenSpec task checkboxes. Deployment manifests, existing UI lifecycle changes, and live source reads/mutations were left untouched as out of scope.",
